page_description: Use this article to learn about using the available web app to chat with Azure OpenAI models.
chunk_content: Web app customizationYou can customize the app's front-end and back-end logic. The app provides several environment variables for common customization scenarios such as changing the icon in the app.When you're customizing the app, we recommend:- Resetting the chat session (clear chat) if users change any settings. Notify the users that their chat history will be lost.- Clearly communicating how each setting that you implement will affect the user experience.- Updating the app settings for each of your deployed apps to use new API keys after you rotate keys for your Azure OpenAI or Azure AI Search resource.Sample source code for the web app is available on GitHub. Source code is provided "as is" and as a sample only. Customers are responsible for all customization and implementation of their web apps.
